The Moon Is Down
       Skyscraper - Defuse Scenario

Counter-Terrorists: 
Hold the skyscraper against an impending
terrorist takeover and prevent the Terrorists
from their destroying the building.

Terrorists: 
Make your way to the skyscraper and plant the
weapon in the lobby area within the building. 
 
Notes: 
-There is one bomb site in this level (between
the trees in the lobby of the skyscraper)
-Designed for 50 players
-See if you can find all weapons in the egg!
